The paper deals with the optimization of resource allocation and interference management in cellular networks, specifically in the context of massive MIMO heterogeneous networks (HetNets). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT), multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems (cs.MM), and system and control theory (cs.SY). Finally, the paper deals with communication systems (cs.COM) and their optimization.
